到非常痛心和惋惜。 碰撞事故发生时，车辆触发车载紧急报警呼叫系统，在多次呼叫用户无反馈后，工作人员第一时间赶往现场支持。结合车辆后台数据初步分析，车辆在行驶过程中未开启辅助驾驶功能，碰撞前 3 秒，车速达到 178km/h，驾驶员采取制动措施，最终以 96km/h 的速度追尾前方卡车，钻入卡车下方后冲出道路。 目前，相关部门已封锁事故现场进行调查处理。我们将配合警方要求提供一切必要数据资料，以便尽快还原事故全貌，同时也将为车主家属提供必要的支持。理想汽车公布广东清远 L7 交通事故相关视频 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1f84d7de81f2346bdba5e9478f3c568a_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636438075"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI1cSCufnmv+M7EAMaCTEwMzcwOTA3MiDJ2qCsBjAAOLYBQApyCTYzNjQzODA3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1703484502.648046", "card_id": "EV_12221333", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年度成长答主来啦，快来看看都是哪些「宝藏答主」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看见在乎的你"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-30f4c5beab07803512ae07501cd2e914.jpg?source=2bcfc003"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/xen/market/ecom-page/1720467485705375744"}, "tag_area": {"normal_url": "", "night_url": "", "width": 0, "height": 0}}, "attached_info": "CnMI1cSCufnmv+M7EBgaBDc4MjIgipWfrAZAC3IIMTIyMjEzMzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZMoBPmh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS94ZW4vbWFya2V0L2Vjb20tcGFnZS8xNzIwNDY3NDg1NzA1Mzc1NzQ0"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1703484502.648075", "card_id": "Q_635790333", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果让你选一个《咒术回战》的术式带到现实，你会选什么？"}, "